frames.caption: A whimsical scene depicts miniature construction workers assembling a stack of donuts as if they were a building project. The workers, dressed in orange safety gear, are positioned around the donuts, using tools and a crane to manage the sugary structure. The playful setup creates an imaginative blend of culinary art and construction work.
frames.description: The scene is a creative and humorous depiction of construction workers interacting with oversized donuts, set against a blurred background. The focus is on the playful interaction between the tiny figures and the large pastries, creating a surreal and imaginative atmosphere.

frames.description: This imaginative scene combines elements of construction and food art, where miniature figures are engaged in building a stack of donuts. The setting is playful and creative, with a focus on the contrast between the small figures and the larger-than-life donuts.
